    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1881-03-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1881-03-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="318" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d318">
                <head>No. 314.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Lowell</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1881-03-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 16,
                            1881</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Have just sent full dispatch to Noyes respecting unfounded and injurious
                        rumors touching our pork product. Noyes will send copy to you. Make most
                        diligent effort to contradict rumors and counteract evil effect.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>BLAINE.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
